      <trans-unit xml:space="preserve" id="786e15c2fa773b34" weblate-flags="md-text, safe-html, strict-same">
        <source>Combat: Corrupt mages blast opponents with beams of energy that blister, slash, and rot flesh, attacking up to three creatures as an action. Many of them have given themselves long claws and teeth that they can use to make up to three melee attacks per action.</source>
